document_data.name: Inn of the Sea Bass
document_data.mainbody: The '''Inn of the Sea Bass''' was located in [[Huzuz]], the City of Delights, along the banks of [[Al-Sarif River]].
document_data.Description: This was a small inn that afforded its inhabitants a splendid view of the [[Caliph's Harbor]].
document_data.Inhabitants: [[Keyfa al-Parid]] lived at the inn so she could be close to her duties at the harbor.
